1) Game Development:
write a game development program that implements the Bubble Sort algorithm. The program will simulate a simple game where the player can input a set of numbers, 
and the numbers 	will be sorted using Bubble Sort to simulate a "level-up" scenario where the player's scores 	are sorted in descending order.*/

PROGRAM:
